222
00:10:17,347 --> 00:10:19,583
UH... Y‐YEAH? THAT'S GREAT!

223
00:10:19,683 --> 00:10:22,852
MASTER SHIROE!
I'M GLAD YOU MADE IT OUT!

224
00:10:22,952 --> 00:10:25,289
UH? OH UH, THANK YOU MINORI.

225
00:10:25,389 --> 00:10:27,657
SO UH, I GUESS
WORK'S BEEN DIFFICULT

226
00:10:27,757 --> 00:10:29,959
(DISAPPOINTED MOO)
YEAH, KIND OF...

227
00:10:31,361 --> 00:10:34,364
[SHIROE] SO THERE'S SOMETHING
I NEED TO TELL ALL OF YOU.

228
00:10:35,099 --> 00:10:35,899
OH YEAH?

229
00:10:35,999 --> 00:10:37,201
OKAY...

230
00:10:37,301 --> 00:10:38,902
WHAT KINDA NEWS IS IT?

231
00:10:39,002 --> 00:10:41,805
RIGHT...
IT'S LIKE THIS...

232
00:10:41,905 --> 00:10:43,940
